OL,3,CAre you the cream of the crop? Island
OL,4,Cdairy farmers hunt for successors
OL,6,FThe remote island of Sark has launched
OL,7,Fthe search for a new farmer to run
OL,8,Ftheir only Community Dairy.
OL,10,FThis comes as the island's original
OL,11,Fdairy farmers, Jason and Katherine
OL,12,FSalisbury, have announced their
OL,13,Fintention to head to pastures new and
OL,14,Freturn to their farm in Suffolk next
OL,15,Fsummer.
