OL,3,CAre you the cream of the crop? Island
OL,4,Cdairy farmers hunt for successors
OL,6,FThe couple 'moo-ved' to Sark in
OL,7,FOctober 2019 following a national
OL,8,Fcampaign to find a farmer who was
OL,9,F'outstanding in their field' and
OL,10,Fpossessed the relevant knowledge and
OL,11,Fexpertise to found Sark's dairy farm.
OL,13,FDuring their time on Sark, the couple
OL,14,Festablished a top-quality herd which
OL,15,Fproduces lines of milk, ice cream,
OL,16,Fbutter, and award-winning cheeses.
OL,18,FThe couple say they are proud of their
OL,19,Fachievements and wish to hand the
OL,20,Fdairy to the next generation.
