OL,3,CAre you the cream of the crop? Island
OL,4,Cdairy farmers hunt for successors
OL,6,FThe 'steaks' are therefore high for
OL,7,Ftheir successors, but the couple says
OL,8,Fthey "would very much like to pass on
OL,9,Four knowledge and help wherever we
OL,10,Fcan".
OL,12,FThey explain: "We hope the newly
OL,13,Fchosen tenants will take the dairy to
OL,14,Fthe next level with the support of the
OL,15,Fislanders."
OL,17,FSeigneur Christopher Beaumont, Trustee
OL,18,Fof Sark's Dairy Trust, says the Dairy
OL,19,Fis "a turnkey business opportunity"
OL,20,Ffor the right person.
