OL,6,FHe adds: "We look forward to hearing
OL,7,Ffrom potential tenants who want to
OL,8,Flive and work in this beautiful
OL,9,Fenvironment."
OL,11,FThe Trust is now hunting for the
OL,12,Fperfect farmer to milk the dairy for
OL,13,Fall it's worth.
OL,15,FThey will begin their search within
OL,16,Fthe two Bailiwicks of Guernsey and
OL,17,FJersey and expand to the UK within the
OL,18,Fnext few weeks.
